Different people have different preferences.  I honestly think Taylor Swift is quite attractive.  However, I personally don't favor many of the women who rank highly on large beauty polls...  For example, I am not particularly attracted to Angelina Jolie, not at all attracted to Kim Kardashian, and am rather turned off by Beyonce, yet all of those women have scored very high in attractiveness polls.  I often meet random people that I find more attractive than most professional super models or celebrity sex idols.  It kind of makes rating attractiveness seem a bit shallow and arbitrary.  Beauty really is in the eye of the beholder.
